title: Led Zeppelin - 1973.07.15 Buffalo, NY
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1973.07.15 Buffalo, NY   

Led Zeppelin
Buffalo, New York
Memorial Auditorium 7-15-73

Source: 
Incomplete excellent soundboard recording.

Details: 
The recording is a very good balanced professional board tape.

1. Rock & Roll
2. Celebration Day
3. Black Dog
4. Over the Hills & Far Away
5. Misty Mountain Hop
6. Since I've Been Loving You
7. No Quarter
8. The Song Remains the Same
9. The Rain Song
10. Dazed & Confused
11. Stairway to Heaven

Comments: 
This show is clearly not one of the best from this tour. Page makes many 
mistakes in Dazed And Confused and Stairway To Heaven sounds by rote a 
hair but during the last hour the whole band seems to be returned from 
sluggishness. Sadly, several huge explosions distract the group 
(especially during the violin bow solo)
